 What could have been spared from the lost and damaged load, was shamelessly carried away within minutes.
Even a motorist stopped to swipe up what was within arms reach from their vehicle door. The truck driver had lost control of his vehicle and veered down the embankment on the side of the highway, leaving the lorry on its side. Also read: #TrafficUpdate – VIDEO: N4 beer spill becomes a free for all! Massyn Vervoer told www.mobeserver.co.za, that the truck was on its way to Nelspruit when the accident occurred.
